  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate Ertapenem Versus It's Comparator in the Treatment of Complicated Intra-abdominal Infections in Adults (0826-050)(COMPLETED)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Multicenter, Open, Randomized, Comparative Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of Ertapenem Versus it's Comparator in the Treatment of Complicated Intra-abdominal Infections in Adults</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This was a prospective, randomized, controlled, open, and multi-center trial conducted to
      compare the clinical efficacy and safety of ertapenem with it's comparator before or
      following adequate surgical management of complicated intra-abdominal infection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
